data.name: Gudfinna
data.description: She was born in a decent family in an important port. She lived free of worries until she was about 14 years old, but at that point things changed.

data.name: Freystein
data.description: He's funny, driven, reliable and perhaps a little too pompous. Which isn't out of the ordinary for someone with his position.

data.name: Ingifast
data.description: He is currently searching for a higher purpose. He feels like there's more than what we get to know in this world. Luckily he has great parents to support him.

data.name: Svartbrand
data.description: While haunted by memories of the past, he now works a small job with low pay. By doing so, he hopes to start life over on a good note and finally find friends he has never had.
